NOTICE
======

This repository contains English translations and community translation data
derived from the CBETA XML-P5 corpus.

Original Source
---------------

CBETA — Chinese Buddhist Electronic Text Association
財團法人佛教電子佛典基金會

Official repository for original texts:
https://github.com/cbeta-org/xml-p5

Original CBETA texts (unmodified) are hosted separately at:
https://github.com/Fabulu/CbetaZenTexts

The translated files in the `xml-p5t` directory are derivative works based on
CBETA XML TEI P5 files. All original CBETA headers are preserved within
each translated file.

License and Usage Condition
---------------------------

CBETA permits redistribution of its XML corpus for NON-COMMERCIAL use,
provided that the full CBETA header remains intact in each file.

This repository complies with that requirement.

All users of this repository must:

- Preserve the original CBETA headers in every translated file
- Maintain non-commercial use of all materials
- Respect CBETA's ownership of the original texts

Translations and Community Data
-------------------------------

The English translations and community data (translation memory, termbases,
reviews) are collaborative works distributed under the same non-commercial
condition as the original CBETA materials.

Independence
------------

This project is an independent translation effort and is not an official
CBETA publication.

If CBETA requests changes regarding attribution or redistribution,
the repository maintainers will comply accordingly.
